Well, the current plan for the Mega-Battle is this: Barclay and Ken on the main table with a total of 3000 points (split however they want) vs. Jim, Wayne and myself with 3500 points total.  Table 2 is Merle with 750-1000 points of Heavy Support (as many ordnance weapons as possible) and 1000 points of other stuff.  He will be allowed to fire ordnance weapons onto the main table, but counts as moving (has to roll to hit).  Keith will be trying to take him out with 1500 points of 13th.  Table 3 is Pyper's Tyranids taking a power planet from Derek at 1000 points apiece.  Still working on a way to get Dave and Johnny involved.<br>
<br>
